CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 10, 1962, pg. 13, reads: "Political Workers in Sixth District of the 13th Ward were (left to right): Mrs. Viola Nollin, Robert Saunders, Mrs. Georgia Paylor, Joseph F. Watts, Democraic [Democratic] committeeman; Mrs. Juanita Jenkins, Mrs. Charlotte Rawlings and George Grisham."
TitMainTitle: Democratic political workers, Viola Nollin, Robert Saunders, Georgia Paylor, Joseph F. Watts, Juanita Jenkins, Charlotte Rawlings, and George Grisham, gathered outside of building with campaign posters
